      "text": [
        " : قُلْتُ اَلْمُحْرِمُ يَشْتَرِي اَلْجَوَارِيَ أَوْ يَبِيعُ فَقَالَ «نَعَمْ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3118 - Sa'd ibn Sa'd al-Ash'ari narrated from Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as).\nHe said: I asked, \"Can a person in the state of Ihram buy or sell slave girls?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes.\""
        ]
      }
